{"General": {"Code": "TAAG", "Type": "Common Stock", "Name": "Awareness Group", "Exchange": "NASDAQ", "CurrencyCode": "USD", "CurrencyName": "US Dollar", "CurrencySymbol": "$", "CountryName": "USA", "CountryISO": "US", "OpenFigi": "BBG000V82CK6", "ISIN": "US35639L1089", "LEI": null, "PrimaryTicker": null, "CUSIP": null, "CIK": null, "EmployerIdNumber": null, "FiscalYearEnd": "September", "IPODate": null, "InternationalDomestic": null, "Sector": "Communication Services", "Industry": "Broadcasting", "GicSector": null, "GicGroup": null, "GicIndustry": null, "GicSubIndustry": null, "HomeCategory": null, "IsDelisted": false, "Description": "The Awareness Group Inc offers TAG GRID, a platform providing solar services and financing solutions for commercial and residential projects. It provides TAG Dealer Program to become sales representative to sell residential and commercial alternative energy projects; TAG Financial to gain access to finance offerings for residential and commercial projects; TAG Distribution for access to pricing on materials; TAG Contractor Program for access to finance and distribution offerings; and TAG Broker Program allows for the opportunity to earn a healthy, residual-based income. The company's TAG Financial operates through two divisions: TAG Financial Services and TAG Capital. Its TAG Financial Services manages the front end of the process, working with sales organizations, providing access to lending products and cutting-edge fintech solutions. Its TAG Capital operates a dynamic in-house fund management, funds proprietary lending products. The Awareness Group Inc was formerly known as Freedom Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to The Awareness Group Inc in October 2025. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is headquartered in Scottsdale, Arizona. The Awareness Group Inc operates as a subsidiary of Medcann Industries, Inc.", "Address": "4343 N Scottsdale Rd, Scottsdale, AZ, United States, 85251", "AddressData": {"Street": "4343 N Scottsda